text: The 1968 Harrow Council election took place on 9 May 1968 to elect members of Harrow London Borough Council in London, England. The whole council was up for election and the Conservative party stayed in overall control of the council. ==Background== ==Election result== ==Ward results== ==References== 1968 Category:1968 London Borough council elections
title: 1968 Harrow London Borough Council election
